'''DigiCert'''公司是一家私人持股，总部于[[美国|美国]]，基于[[X.509|X.509]]的[[傳輸層安全協議|SSL]][[数字证书认证机构|数字证书认证机构]]（CA）。作为一个{{tsl|en|Trusted third party|可信第三方}}，DigiCert为[[网页浏览器|网页浏览器]]核验网站所有方的身份。

作为[[CA/浏览器论坛|CA/浏览器论坛]]（设立公共信任数字证书行业标准的组织<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cabforum.org/about-us/|title=About the CA/Browser Forum|accessdate=2015-12-25|publisher=CAB Forum|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127054350/https://cabforum.org/about-us/|dead-url=no}}</ref>）的创始成员，DigiCert促进了[[扩展验证证书|扩展验证证书]]（EV）的发展。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cabforum.org/forum.html|title=About the CA/Browser Forum|accessdate=2015-12-25|publisher=CAB Forum|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070202031218/http://www.cabforum.org/forum.html|archive-date=2007-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>DigiCert也与[[微软|微软]]合作开发和促进SSL中的[[主题备用名称|主题备用名称]]，用于在[[Microsoft_Exchange_Server|Microsoft Exchange Server]]中使用。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/929395 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-02-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123060057/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/929395 |archivedate=2009-01-23 }}</ref>

DigiCert是最大的不直接颁发域名验证（DV）SSL证书的公共CA。它主要销售组织验证（OV）和扩展验证（EV）的SSL证书。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digicert.com/dv-ssl-certificate.htm|title=Domain Validated SSL? Why We Don't Offer It|accessdate=2015-12-25|date=2009-02-19|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305033533/https://www.digicert.com/dv-ssl-certificate.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

DigiCert公司与[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]的证书颁发机构Digicert Sdn. Bhd没有任何关系，该机构使用弱密钥颁发证书，因而其信任已被众[[网页浏览器|网页浏览器]]撤销。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.entrust.net/advisories/malaysia.htm|title=SSL Certificate Support - Entrust, Inc|accessdate=2015-12-25|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629012844/http://www.entrust.net/advisories/malaysia.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.mozilla.org/security/2011/11/03/revoking-trust-in-digicert-sdn-bhd-intermediate-certificate-authority/ |title=Revoking Trust in DigiCert Sdn. |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2012-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929035007/http://blog.mozilla.org/security/2011/11/03/revoking-trust-in-digicert-sdn-bhd-intermediate-certificate-authority/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/security/advisory/2641690 Microsoft Security Advisory (2641690)] {{Wayback|url=http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/security/advisory/2641690 |date=20130708102648 }} "DigiCert Sdn.</ref>

== 历史 ==
DigiCert由{{tsl|en|Ken Bretschneider}}成立于2003年。他在2012年被评选进入[[安永|安永]]企业家奖年度决赛。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digicert.com/news/entrepreneur-of-the-year-2012.htm|title=Entrepreneur of the Year 2012|accessdate=July 9, 2014|archive-date=2017-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170503033832/https://www.digicert.com/news/entrepreneur-of-the-year-2012.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.peoplewater.com/ken-bretschneiders-nomination-for-entrepreneur-of-the-year|title=Ken Bretschneider’s Nomination for Entrepreneur of the Year|accessdate=July 9, 2014|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=July 14, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140530152827/http://www.peoplewater.com/ken-bretschneiders-nomination-for-entrepreneur-of-the-year|archivedate=2014年5月30日}}</ref>他担任[[董事会|董事会]]的[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]和[[董事长|董事长]]，直至2012年离开到{{tsl|en|People Water}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/people-water-names-ken-bretschneider-ceo-148631965.html|title=People Water Names Ken Bretschneider CEO|accessdate=July 9, 2014|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=April 24, 2012|archive-date=2017-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701152311/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/people-water-names-ken-bretschneider-ceo-148631965.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并由Nicholas Hales代替。<ref name="stepsdown">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/money/53925270-79/digicert-hales-bretschneider-growth.html.csp|title=Utah's DigiCert reorganizes its management|accessdate=July 9, 2012|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=April 17, 2012|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215955/http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/money/53925270-79/digicert-hales-bretschneider-growth.html.csp|dead-url=no}}</ref>DigiCert目前由[[私募|私募]]股权公司Thoma Bravo持有多数股权，TA Associates持有少数股权。Thoma Bravo于2015年8月28日收购了DigiCert的多数股权，这是迄今为止总部位于[[犹他州|犹他州]]的最大的公司投资之一，他称“DigiCert是一个代表市场领导者的杰出的投资机会，以其一贯的创新和一流的客户服务闻名。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eweek.com/security/thoma-bravo-invests-in-security-firm-digicert.html|title=Thoma Bravo Invests in Security Firm DigiCert|accessdate=2015-12-25|author=Sean Michael Kerner|date=2015-08-28}}</ref>

2017年8月2日，DigiCert以9.5亿美元现金和DigiCert业务的30%股权收购[[赛门铁克|赛门铁克]]安全认证业务(CA)。

